"snippet" : "Variable The array index of the list entry that the user clicks is saved at runtime. Variable (integer data type) Example: PLC_PRG.iIndexComboboxEntry Data array Displayed as a combo box. Every array component becomes a combo box entry. Array variable ( ARRAY[...] OF ) Example: PLC_PRG.astrCombobox ...", 
