"snippet" : "Add node Symbol: Function : Adds a new property in the frame configuration, in the tree view of the interface properties Call : Visualization menu, context menu Requirement : The focus is in the Frame configuration tab. The property is added to the bottom of the tree view. Double-click the new entry...", 
